Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.47,0:00:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要上囉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.18,0:00:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}阿諾斯大人應援歌合唱曲 第二
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.94,0:00:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一 二 三 四
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.74,0:00:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\an8}承蒙高貴的阿諾斯大人的寶劍♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.59,0:00:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\an8}在名為鬥技場的床鋪上♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.94,0:00:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\an8}獵物起舞♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.33,0:00:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奧義 水牙連魔突
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.10,0:00:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\an8}你在下♪ 我在上♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.13,0:00:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\an8}秒殺♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.87,0:00:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}剛好一分鐘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.03,0:01:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}確認魔劍損壞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.82,0:01:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\an8}漏洞百出 漏洞百出 漏洞百出
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.24,0:01:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}勝者是阿諾斯·福爾迪哥德
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.44,0:01:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}阿諾斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.37,0:01:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好厲害啊阿諾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.40,0:01:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}為什麼? 為什麼我會被那種程度的劍…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.57,0:01:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真正的名匠飽含真心鍛造出的劍裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.35,0:01:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}蘊藏著魔力以外的某樣東西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.41,0:01:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不要小瞧我父親的劍了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.08,0:01:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你聽到了嗎? 剛才的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.17,0:01:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那傢伙的父親 到底是什麼人啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.32,0:01:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}阿諾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.26,0:01:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}兄長大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.60,0:01:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}阿諾斯·福爾迪哥德
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.66,0:03:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太精彩了 阿諾斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.93,0:03:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沒什麼 才第一回合而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.87,0:03:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}第一回合 第二場比賽已決出勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.65,0:03:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}勝者是羅格諾斯魔劍協會所屬的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.09,0:03:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}雷·古蘭茲德利
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.22,0:03:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}羅格諾斯?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.73,0:03:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那不是皇族派的組織嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.83,0:03:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我希望你能什麼都不要問
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.58,0:03:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}雖然我是可以
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.70,0:03:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}為什麼要加入羅格諾斯魔劍協會?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.27,0:03:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}皇族派對你說了什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.86,0:03:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.91,0:03:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也許對我說了 可以給我能玩兒一輩子的錢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.23,0:03:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}和魔皇的寶座吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.59,0:03:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我不覺得你會因為那種事動搖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.82,0:03:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}現在的我是皇族派的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.25,0:04:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}已經沒辦法和你們好好相處了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.18,0:04:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}還有件事忘了說了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.24,0:04:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}阿諾斯 我會殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.38,0:04:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那麼 就抱著必死的決心來挑戰我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.43,0:04:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這可威脅不到我 我本來就是拼上了性命的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.37,0:04:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是嗎? 那麼你的決心 就讓我來測試一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.09,0:04:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}阿諾斯大人? 雷同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.42,0:04:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我本來可是想把你的頭連著手腕一起砍下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.78,0:04:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我本來也是想捏碎你的心臟的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.89,0:04:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}身體也很結實啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.23,0:04:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.14,0:04:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯 決賽再見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.05,0:04:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}阿諾斯大人?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.06,0:04:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}看來他是被套上了項圈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.71,0:04:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.72,0:04:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}雷的體內存在著魔法道具的觸感
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.73,0:04:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}恐怕是契約的魔劍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.92,0:05:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}應該是在某種條件下會毀滅根源的機關吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.78,0:05:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎麼會?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.57,0:05:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他沒有直接向我求救
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.03,0:05:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可能是因為有人質在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.70,0:05:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}比如住院中的母親
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.92,0:05:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}勝者 阿諾斯·福爾迪哥德
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.94,0:05:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\an8}進入決賽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.96,0:05:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不愧是阿諾斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.51,0:05:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那傢伙 這樣下去明天的決賽不會也能取勝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.74,0:05:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沒事 雷·古蘭茲德利也贏了下來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.56,0:05:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也是啊 那傢伙的話一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.99,0:05:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}預備
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.54,0:05:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}阿諾斯大人 恭喜您進入決賽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.82,0:05:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好厲害 天才 太帥了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.25,0:05:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}做得好啊阿諾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.11,0:05:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}父親大人也很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.08,0:05:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}賭在劍上的思念跟別人不一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.36,0:05:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不愧是真正的名匠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.22,0:05:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哎呀 是嗎? 哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.96,0:05:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.92,0:05:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}蘊藏著思念確實並不假
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.38,0:05:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.47,0:05:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哎呀 我得回去工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.01,0:06:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}明天我還會來為你加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.22,0:06:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}忙的話 看魔法廣播就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.02,0:06:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}說什麼呢 這可是你的大舞台啊 再見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.49,0:06:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一路走好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.45,0:06:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我也去辦一點事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.67,0:06:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那那把劍 媽媽我先幫你拿著吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.84,0:06:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}還挺重的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.50,0:06:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}為了明天 你多少也得休息下才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.94,0:06:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且 畢竟是很重要的劍嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.93,0:06:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}的確 規則上並不承認用別的劍替代
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.52,0:06:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}母親
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.60,0:06:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.20,0:06:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沒 沒關係 沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.49,0:06:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不論發生什麼我都會保護這把劍的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.22,0:06:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我們也會一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.08,0:06:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那就交給你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.61,0:06:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}請交給我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.56,0:06:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這位就是雷同學的… 身體…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.31,0:06:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}精靈病嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.16,0:06:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}魔力微弱 根源也很稀薄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.38,0:07:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這樣下去肯定會消滅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.57,0:07:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.73,0:07:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真奇怪啊 看起來倒是跟衰老的狀態很相似
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.27,0:07:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不對 並不是純粹的魔族嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.10,0:07:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.94,0:07:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在魔族和精靈之間誕生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.29,0:07:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}跟你一樣是半靈半魔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.25,0:07:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是 雷同學是皇族啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.44,0:07:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}母親應該是純血的魔族吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.73,0:07:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}估計是親生父母和撫養的人不一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.61,0:07:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這樣的話 精靈病應該看作是半靈半魔特有的病嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.97,0:07:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}阿諾斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.54,0:07:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你就是阿諾斯同學?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.74,0:07:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}為什麼你知道我?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.76,0:07:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我的意識還是一直存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.17,0:07:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}雷一直在這裡聊著你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.55,0:07:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}說是交到了朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.42,0:07:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}雷的體內刺有契約的魔劍這件事呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.27,0:07:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.86,0:07:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他為了換來我的治療 對皇族言聽計從
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.11,0:08:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}能治好你的話雷就不受枷鎖束縛了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.28,0:08:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}關於精靈病你知道些什麼嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.67,0:08:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}精靈是某人的思念 願望 傳聞或傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.96,0:08:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那些具現化的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.48,0:08:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是 作為半靈半魔根源的傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.34,0:08:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是剛剛誕生的弱小傳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.72,0:08:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那傳聞很容易消失
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.11,0:08:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}消失多少 就會將根源磨損多少
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.77,0:08:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那麼 只要傳播那傳說就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.79,0:08:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你的傳說是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.66,0:08:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.01,0:08:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是 今天力量稍微恢復了一些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.97,0:08:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我都不知道這是時隔多久再次說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.48,0:08:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你的傳說在某處傳播開來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.08,0:08:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}緩和了你的症狀嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.08,0:08:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是這保持不了多久了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.20,0:08:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在那之前 我有事想要告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.19,0:08:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.75,0:08:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}雷從以前開始就非常喜歡劍術
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.51,0:08:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一有空就總是在揮劍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:08:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是 他看起來總是很無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.17,0:09:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}又贏了比賽嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.13,0:09:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}雷真是個強大的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.35,0:09:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}強大是件好事嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.78,0:09:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.63,0:09:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要是我更加弱小的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就能什麼都不用在意 盡情地揮劍了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.78,0:09:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}自我倒下以來他好像就越來越孤獨了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.20,0:09:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.40,0:09:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}母親 我今天輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.92,0:09:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}輸得非常徹底
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.02,0:09:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}很奇怪吧 他居然那麼開心地說自己輸了的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.86,0:09:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}想要和你盡情戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.41,0:09:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就是那孩子的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.84,0:09:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}拜託了 阿諾斯同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.79,0:09:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}請將雷釋放出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.13,0:09:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}請不要讓那孩子揮舞卑鄙的劍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.50,0:09:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真的可以嗎? 你會無法得救的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.85,0:09:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我沒有想過為了活下去 還要拖累孩子的後腿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.89,0:09:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎麼會 那也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.42,0:09:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}阿諾斯大人 沒有什麼辦法嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.03,0:10:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}無法知道傳說的話 就很難痊癒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.63,0:10:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}精靈和魔族的根源是不一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.25,0:10:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就算分出我的性命 也沒有辦法救下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.09,0:10:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}同為半靈半魔的我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.86,0:10:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}接下來我將連接你們的根源
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.70,0:10:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}米薩 你要使用精靈魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.55,0:10:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}消耗自己的根源
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.87,0:10:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那個時候所產生的 傳聞和傳說帶來的回復力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.58,0:10:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我會分給希拉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.89,0:10:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}還有那種魔法嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.02,0:10:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我現做的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.26,0:10:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.29,0:10:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是最差的情況 你們兩個都會毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.37,0:10:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因為根源消耗過多的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.25,0:10:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就無法甦生了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.98,0:10:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不行 我不能讓你做那麼危險的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.42,0:10:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我要做 請讓我做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.92,0:10:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.22,0:10:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}雷同學沒有必要被牽扯進 統一派或皇族派的鬥爭之中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.53,0:10:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.11,0:10:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我相信阿諾斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.70,0:11:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}米薩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.59,0:11:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.05,0:11:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}暫時很順利
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.16,0:11:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.60,0:11:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是效率很低
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.51,0:11:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你會先迎來極限
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.68,0:11:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是如果多少能恢復一些的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.91,0:11:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎麼了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.24,0:11:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}然後啊 店門也是阿諾斯做的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.23,0:11:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}阿諾斯大人親手做的門
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.74,0:11:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好想被夾~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.70,0:11:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}伊莎貝拉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.35,0:11:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}艾米莉亞老師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.70,0:11:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}請問有什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.87,0:12:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}其實有一條規定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.77,0:12:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}決賽需要由運營委員會暫時保管選手的劍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.93,0:12:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有那種規定來著嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.14,0:12:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.85,0:12:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那麼 我就先收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.57,0:12:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.61,0:12:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因為這是阿諾斯委託給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.43,0:12:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我會直接送去運營委員會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.05,0:12:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真頭疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.63,0:12:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}艾米莉亞老師?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.18,0:12:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}快點交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.21,0:12:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不然的話 你會很慘的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.63,0:12:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}請放開
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.42,0:12:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.37,0:12:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那就請你和那把劍一起去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.96,0:12:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}母親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.06,0:12:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}休想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你都做了些什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.98,0:13:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}她們是你重要的學生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.05,0:13:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}學生?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.47,0:13:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}混血不過是偷聽課程的小偷罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.08,0:13:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}比起那種事 請快點把劍交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.48,0:13:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.86,0:13:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}讓身為純血的路德威爾家蒙羞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.22,0:13:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎麼可能得到原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.14,0:13:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}區區混血
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.98,0:13:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奪走劍讓他無法出場是不對的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.97,0:13:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你們沒有作為皇族出生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.00,0:13:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}本身就是不對的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.70,0:13:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.83,0:13:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}母親大人 請快逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.94,0:13:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不行 大家也要一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.79,0:13:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.32,0:13:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因為我們有八個人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.62,0:13:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你們等我 我會叫人來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.33,0:13:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}無力又愚蠢的你們所做的事 都是沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.89,0:13:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}才不是 沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.05,0:14:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}才不是 愚蠢的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.08,0:14:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我們要保護 阿諾斯大人重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.21,0:14:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我們要保護
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.02,0:14:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.29,0:14:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以我都說了是沒用的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.59,0:14:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}秒殺♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.11,0:14:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}輕鬆♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.42,0:14:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}能請你們閉嘴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.83,0:14:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}承蒙高貴的♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.62,0:14:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}阿諾斯大人的寶劍♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.52,0:14:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我叫你們閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.07,0:14:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在名為鬥技場的床鋪上♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.74,0:14:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.74,0:14:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}獵物起舞♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.78,0:14:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你在下♪ 我在上♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.20,0:14:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}混血才在皇族之下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.62,0:14:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.75,0:14:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}得到教訓了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.83,0:15:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這就是混血的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.15,0:15:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}還真是熱衷於教育啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.66,0:15:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}阿諾斯 大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.16,0:15:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這是你的低賤導致的結果吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.94,0:15:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}搞清楚你的立場…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.88,0:15:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.00,0:15:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}治癒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.75,0:15:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}阿諾斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.21,0:15:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}告訴我你們的名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.49,0:15:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}艾 艾蓮·米海斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.77,0:15:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我叫傑西卡·阿涅特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.56,0:15:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}雪莉雅·尼潔姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.43,0:15:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}希亞·明先
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.37,0:15:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}艾蓮 傑西卡 雪莉雅 希亞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.37,0:15:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}西姆卡·霍拉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.29,0:15:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}邁雅·潔姆特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.92,0:16:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}卡 卡薩·庫爾諾亞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.05,0:16:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}諾諾·依諾塔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.91,0:16:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}西姆卡 邁雅 卡薩 諾諾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.90,0:16:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你們的名字 我一輩子都不會忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.41,0:16:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}辛苦你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.17,0:16:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}母親
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.68,0:16:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}之後拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.56,0:16:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.42,0:16:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喂 艾米莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.78,0:16:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我是很寬容的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.81,0:16:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我一直覺得自己不會聽任憤怒 做出愚蠢的行為
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.26,0:16:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哎呀 真是個巨大的錯誤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.24,0:16:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}艾米莉亞 我無法原諒你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.06,0:16:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那麼 讓你受到致命傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.89,0:16:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}估計最多只剩一分鐘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.93,0:16:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎麼樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.11,0:17:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果承認我是暴虐的魔王 向我求饒的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.67,0:17:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我說不定會改變主意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.57,0:17:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}誰要 對你這種低俗又不中用的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.64,0:17:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}住 住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.68,0:17:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你說什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.75,0:17:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}請住手… 救 救命…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.37,0:17:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}更大聲地說說看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.54,0:17:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}暴 暴虐的魔王阿諾斯·福爾迪哥德大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.85,0:17:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}還請寬恕我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.57,0:17:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不要說不由衷的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.68,0:17:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}騙子就要下地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.41,0:17:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.92,0:17:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}魔族煉成
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.24,0:17:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.32,0:17:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}脫胎換骨的感覺怎麼樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.39,0:17:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你 你是想這樣就算羞辱我嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.31,0:17:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}下賤的混血
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.80,0:17:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}下賤的混血嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.79,0:17:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}艾米莉亞 你要自以為是皇族到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.10,0:17:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.57,0:18:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}用你的魔眼看看深淵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.48,0:18:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}混血…?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.11,0:18:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎麼會… 騙人…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.19,0:18:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真的是混血?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.22,0:18:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不對 不對
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.87,0:18:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.17,0:18:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我對你下了詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.35,0:18:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不論死去多少次 都會轉世成為混血的詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.59,0:18:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.24,0:18:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在不同的立場上 重新審視這個國家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.44,0:18:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}說不定意外地 你會注意到自己思想的差錯有多大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.68,0:18:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎麼會 不要 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.07,0:18:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}為什麼你會在這?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.60,0:18:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}對 對不起 我擅自…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.20,0:18:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這魔法是? 是在分享你的力量嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.24,0:18:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.60,0:18:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因為我怎麼也不覺得 雷同學會成為皇族派
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.71,0:19:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我是個騙子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.78,0:19:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}雷同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.19,0:19:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果母親能夠治好的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.76,0:19:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你就沒必要遵從皇族派了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.03,0:19:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你真是個不得了的好人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.24,0:19:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}阿諾斯知道這件事嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.76,0:19:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.63,0:19:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.08,0:19:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}還是稍微休息一下比較好吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.88,0:19:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你的根源也在磨損吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.02,0:19:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.75,0:19:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}再好好考慮一下比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.07,0:19:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不要被無趣的感傷帶跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.89,0:19:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}無趣的感傷 嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.72,0:19:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你加入統一派應該是為了拯救更多的混血
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.31,0:19:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那麼有一天 會有真的需要你賭上性命的日子到來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.46,0:19:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}已經來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.29,0:19:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我不能等到有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.01,0:19:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}現在就想多拯救哪怕一個在痛苦的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.64,0:19:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果不這麼想的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.08,0:19:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就算有一天來了 也一定無法賭上性命的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.31,0:19:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你真是強大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.56,0:19:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.81,0:20:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這樣下去你也會很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.19,0:20:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我卻沒有馬上阻止你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.65,0:20:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.14,0:20:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}雷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.10,0:20:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}母親?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.54,0:20:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}雷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.57,0:20:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}母親
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.85,0:20:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等著我 我一定會取得優勝的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.08,0:20:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.28,0:20:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.35,0:20:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.25,0:20:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我全都知道的 不用在意我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.24,0:20:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}您在說什麼呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.21,0:20:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}能夠和你相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.80,0:20:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}媽媽我僅此而已就足夠幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.17,0:20:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你這不中用的東西 才不是我家的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.57,0:20:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}給我出去 丟人的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.96,0:20:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}媽媽我不論何時都站在你這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.27,0:20:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}請你保持自己的風格
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.87,0:20:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}自由地活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.50,0:21:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}母親? 母親
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.97,0:21:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}各位久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.83,0:21:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}接下來就將開始迪爾海德魔劍大會的決賽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.09,0:21:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好好享受
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.64,0:21:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯 我去去就來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.87,0:21:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}阿諾斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.51,0:21:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.15,0:21:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都到這一步了就要拿下優勝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.78,0:23:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}下集 兩人的決賽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.30,0:01:54.58,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord0}{\c&HEBC4EA&}現実逃避の脳内で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.58,0:01:57.01,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord0}{\c&HFBF5B1&}安寧の夢むさぼって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.01,0:02:01.67,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord0}{\c&HBEC1FD&}呑気な平和がいつまでも続くって信じきっている
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.67,0:02:06.23,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur4\bord4}{\3c&HD37427&}現在陳腐な常識も 平俗凡愚な限界も
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.23,0:02:11.00,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur4\bord4}{\3c&HAD034D&}「全くもって下らないね」なの言ってんのはいったいどいつ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.00,0:02:15.53,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur4\bord4}{\3c&H1D2049&}かすれてく記憶の彼方で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.53,0:02:20.33,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur4\bord4}{\3c&H1D2049&}ねじ曲げられてく 遥かな約束
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.33,0:02:24.89,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur4\bord4}{\3c&H85880C&}誰も皆忘れているなら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.89,0:02:31.22,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur4\bord4\fs40\pos(655,1000)}{\3c&H85880C&}まなこ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.89,0:02:31.22,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur4\bord4}{\3c&H85880C&}眼を開いて 思い出させてやる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.38,0:02:36.14,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur4\bord4}{\3c&HAD034D&}超えてゆくのさ 残酷な世界を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.14,0:02:40.68,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur4\bord4}{\3c&H2676F9&}誓い合ったあの日の儚い希望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.68,0:02:45.45,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur4\bord4}{\3c&HD37427&}蹴り上げてやれ キミの痛みを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.45,0:02:50.04,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur4\bord4}{\3c&HFE2EB8&}全てを飲み込むその業火で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.04,0:02:54.77,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur4\bord4}{\3c&HFE2EB8&}正解不正解 可能不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.77,0:03:01.38,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur4\bord4}{\3c&HFE2EB8&}全ては この手の中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.30,0:01:54.58,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord0}{\c&HEBC4EA&}在逃避現實的腦中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.58,0:01:57.01,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord0}{\c&HFBF5B1&}做著貪圖安寧的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.01,0:02:01.67,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord0}{\c&HBEC1FD&}堅信無憂無慮的和平會永遠持續下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.67,0:02:06.23,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur4\bord4}{\3c&HD37427&}現在那陳舊的常識 平凡庸俗的界限
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.23,0:02:11.00,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur4\bord4}{\3c&HAD034D&}「真拿你沒辦法啊」你到底在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.00,0:02:15.53,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur4\bord4}{\3c&H1D2049&}在模糊記憶的彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.53,0:02:20.33,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur4\bord4}{\3c&H1D2049&}被扭曲的遙遠約定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.33,0:02:24.89,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur4\bord4}{\3c&H85880C&}若把每一個人都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.89,0:02:31.22,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur4\bord4}{\3c&H85880C&}就睜開雙眼 讓我回想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.38,0:02:36.14,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur4\bord4}{\3c&HAD034D&}互相起誓的那天虛假的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.14,0:02:40.68,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur4\bord4}{\3c&H2676F9&}跨越這個殘酷的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.68,0:02:45.45,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur4\bord4}{\3c&HD37427&}就用吞噬一切的業火
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.45,0:02:50.04,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur4\bord4}{\3c&HFE2EB8&}將你的痛楚一腳踢開
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.04,0:02:54.77,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur4\bord4}{\3c&HFE2EB8&}正確與錯誤 可能與不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.77,0:03:01.38,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur4\bord4}{\3c&HFE2EB8&}全都掌握於手中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.20,0:22:30.21,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}{\fad(250,250)}際限ない争いの行く先は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.69,0:22:39.24,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}{\fad(250,250)}本当の僕らの命の価値を見出せるかい?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.40,0:22:43.30,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}{\fad(250,250)}真っ白で名も無い ラベルを貼られていた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.30,0:22:46.88,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}{\fad(250,250)}中身なんて無いも同然で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.07,0:22:50.82,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}{\fad(250,250)}自らをも犠牲に 幸せを願った
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.82,0:22:56.33,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}{\fad(250,250)}君の強さは僕が知っている
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.40,0:23:01.53,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}{\fad(250,250)}{\3c&H681E01&\4c&H681E01&}ハミダシモノの声よ響け
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.70,0:23:06.81,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}{\fad(250,250)}{\3c&H681E01&\4c&H681E01&}震える手を引いて その先へと向かおう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.81,0:23:12.56,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}{\fad(250,250)}{\3c&H681E01&\4c&H681E01&}僕が望んだ景色を君に見せるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.56,0:23:16.82,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}{\fad(250,250)}{\3c&H036131&\4c&H036131&}涙に負けた夜を壊せ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.82,0:23:21.97,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}{\fad(250,250)}{\3c&H036131&\4c&H036131&}弱さ悔しさも全て力にして
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.97,0:23:29.32,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}{\fad(250,250)}{\3c&H036131&\4c&H036131&}掴め 見せつけろ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.20,0:22:30.21,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}{\fad(250,250)}無止無盡的衝突的目的地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.69,0:22:39.24,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}{\fad(250,250)}能找到我們生命的真正價值嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.40,0:22:43.30,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}{\fad(250,250)}繡著純白無名的標章
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.30,0:22:46.88,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}{\fad(250,250)}內容什麼的簡直跟沒有一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.07,0:22:50.82,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}{\fad(250,250)}犧牲奉獻自己 也祝願著幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.82,0:22:56.33,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}{\fad(250,250)}你的強大我都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.40,0:23:01.53,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}{\fad(250,250)}{\3c&H681E01&\4c&H681E01&}充斥被排除之人的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.70,0:23:06.81,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}{\fad(250,250)}{\3c&H681E01&\4c&H681E01&}拉著顫動的雙手勇往直前吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.81,0:23:12.56,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}{\fad(250,250)}{\3c&H681E01&\4c&H681E01&}讓你看看我所期望的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.56,0:23:16.82,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}{\fad(250,250)}{\3c&H036131&\4c&H036131&}讓敗給淚水的夜晚毀滅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.82,0:23:21.97,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}{\fad(250,250)}{\3c&H036131&\4c&H036131&}軟弱與懊悔全部轉化為力量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.97,0:23:29.32,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}{\fad(250,250)}{\3c&H036131&\4c&H036131&}抓住後就讓我看看
